<LocalizedProperties><Language>en</Language><Title>Security Update for Exchange 2000 Server Service Pack 3 (KB959897)</Title><Description>A security issue has been identified that could allow an unauthenticated remote attacker to compromise your Microsoft Exchange 2000 Server Service Pack 3 systems and gain control over them. You can help protect your computer by installing this update from Microsoft. After you install this item, you may have to restart your computer.</Description><UninstallNotes>Uninstall is available from "Add or Remove Programs" in the Control Panel</UninstallNotes><MoreInfoUrl>http://support.microsoft.com/?kbid=959897</MoreInfoUrl><SupportUrl>http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=138928</SupportUrl></LocalizedProperties>